title: Bonus Ep4: Heaux Tales & Regrets Snippet
itunes:title: Bonus Ep4: Heaux Tales & Regrets Snippet
description:
So we decided to share a snippet from our last bonus episode where we discuss things that we have regret over the years. We discuss the infamous fight that lead to our friendship, men we regret sleeping or being with, and Mandii shares a story of stealing a lap top and phones over a fly out gone wrong. The Patrons seem to have enjoyed this episode and we hope you will too. To hear more of this episode and previous bonus episodes, you can become a patron at Patreon.com/whoreibledecisions. Patrons receive bonus episodes, full video footage to most episodes, and more! Become apart of the #whorehive today!
